sourcesContent: import React, {Component} from 'react' import {Grid,Card, Icon, Image, List } from 'semantic-ui-react' class Places extends Component { render(){ const list = this.props.venues.map((venue,i)=> {venue.name} Joined in 2015 Matthew is a musician living in Nashville. 22 Friends ) console.log("look for pic", this.props.venues.map(venue => console.log("category", ))) return ( {list} ) } } export default Places
